title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Virgin Slopo Topo
description:
Join forces with the kings and eat all day. The Core 4 are absolutely radiating positive vibes for our best friends behind the paywall this week, discussing the secret history of The Only Podcast That Matters™, recapping our latest mature and tasteful corporate outing in celebration of joining the 1 million downloads club, gorp life activation, the parental qualities of the gd mf boyz, raising a generation of Throw Gang, having children, being big brothers and much more.
